name: 'Brendon Ng'
bio: 'I love to cook flavorful main course entrees

name: 'Jivan Gubbi'
bio: 'Hello! My name is Jivan and I am a baker who is passionate about sourdough. I sell all things sourdough from bread to cookies to pancakes!'

name: 'Shikha Mody'
bio: 'I love baking new types of breads and desserts ranging from traditional banana bread to chocolate souffles! I am very aware of dietary restrictions and do my best to adjust to everyone’s needs. My favorite dishes to make are choux buns (cream puffs) and chocolate cake!'

name: 'Armaan Singh'
shortDesc: I’m Armaan! I love baking and cooking a little bit of everything
location: especially breakfast food and larger entrees. Currently working on the perfect chocolate chip cookie recipe.'
